```

The `s1ap_Cause_t` is defined as an enum in `/repo/openair2/COMMON/s1ap_messages_types.h`:
```c
typedef enum {
  S1AP_CAUSE_RADIO_NETWORK,
  S1AP_CAUSE_TRANSPORT,
  S1AP_CAUSE_NAS,
